values: Three days ago was erin and mines 2 month anniversary... i love you so much. i miss talkin to you. today i went to NARA for the best sushi in the town. i cant wait till tomorow...waves are supposed to be good. SCORE!!!! finally, on the way home i had to drive my mom, sister her friend barrett and her older sister... that was fun, girls are CRAZY!... any way now im rockin out to christmas music...Trans Siberian Orchestra style...i need sleep. -later

hey guys...4days a go i was asked to go to occoquan to row in the MV4. the row was pretty shity but atleast we pulled in a fourth place finish. other than that while i was up at occ. i went to FYE and got the story of the year cd...its awesome. oh ya!! i was stoked to find skate and surf stuff in northern virginia, only because while i was at the mall i only saw gothic kids, wiggers, and VERY prepy kids. oh my god! i almost forgot about wut happened at the hotel... RUSSIAN FEAR FACTOR except way more intense. for example... a girl was about to win so they put her in a car to answer the final "?" and *joe goes i bet they blow up the car* right before she got a word out the front of the car BLOWS the f**k UP!!! it was so funny, and to add to that then 10 guys come out of left field and beat the hell out of the rest of the car. after that erin called and i talked to her for a while(god i missed you). on the way home from the race we stopped at OLD COUNTRY BUFFET hell yea the food sucked...exuse me SUCKS!! but i hit up the ice cream machine, that kicked ass...for OCB ice cream. well thats about all of my weekend i have to go do yrad work now, so later!

ONE MONTH today with erin... i love you baby! hell yea i got my license today, im so stoked!!! anyways besides that im going to occoquan as a rower in matt defoore's spot...pussy, jk. i hope we stop at golden corrall, i love that place...x-treme gulp-DZZZZZZZZ-hahahahahaha! oh my god i wonder if davis will be there, that little kid was all about grabbing some butt meat. on top of that he was a coach snead as a little kid. i am so full i just got done anihilating some outback steakhouse. iight i have to go finish packing for occoquan... later peeps

hey...bush won, anyway school sucks mostly mrs walkers class *chemistry*. english was chill b/c all we did was take a test. crackdougal was flippin out today. , it was hilarious!!! i hope i pass the behind the wheel test, god i would love to get my license so i wouldnt have to rely on my rents all the time. on top of that i just wanna be able to be free from ridin the dreaded "cheesewagon" lol...i hate the bus its always so f'ing late and my bus driver drives like he's qualifying for the daytona 500. anyways i really just wanna be able to hang out with all my friends, mostly erin. i love you baby! well i have to go... drivers ed is on the way. -later

wut up, i almost have my license...ill finally be able to go see my baby erin and go surfing when i want. *random* titans are 3-5... im really tired right now so im gonna "hit the hay" hahaha old school... later
